{"product_id":"sadaf-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Sadaf Attar (Roll On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e  Discover the calm and elegant fragrance of Sadaf Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSadaf is a smooth and pleasant attar with a soft, fresh, and mildly sweet aroma, perfect for those who prefer subtle and balanced fragrances.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is designed for daily wear, prayer, office use, and light occasions. Its alcohol-free formulation makes it gentle on the skin while providing a long-lasting and soothing scent throughout the day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Soft, Fresh \u0026amp; Pleasant\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting \u0026amp; Smooth Aroma\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for men \u0026amp; women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Sadaf Attar\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLight and elegant fragrance for everyday use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNon-irritating and skin-friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCalm, refreshing aroma without being overpowering\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging, suitable for gifting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply lightly on pulse points such as the neck, wrists, or behind the ears for a lasting and refreshing fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472867922167,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/CA5E3F72-5228-4809-9296-A4247510D771.png?v=1777870289","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/sadaf-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider